getClientFeedback(uint256,address).details: Get all feedback from a specific client for an agent

returns._0: Array of all feedback from that client

params.client: The address of the client who gave feedback

params.tag: Search for this tag in either tag1 or tag2

returns._0: Filtered array of feedback matching the tag

getFeedbackCount(uint256,address).details: Get the number of feedback entries from a specific client

getSummary(uint256,address[]).details: Get aggregated reputation summary for an agent from specified clients

params.clients: Array of client addresses to include in summary

returns.totalValue: Sum of all non-revoked feedback values

params.decimals: Number of decimal places for the value
params.value: The feedback value (can be negative for poor performance)

returns._0: feedbackIndex The index of the feedback

params.feedbackIndex: The index of the feedback to revoke
